1
00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:37,079
Just try laying a finger on my godfather!

2
00:00:37,240 --> 00:00:38,039
Throw your weapons over here.

3
00:00:38,039 --> 00:00:39,079
Let my godfather go.

4
00:00:39,079 --> 00:00:40,439
An Xiang, don't do anything rash.

5
00:00:40,439 --> 00:00:41,240
Put the knife down.

6
00:00:41,719 --> 00:00:42,399
Put the knife down.

7
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:44,359
You throw your weapons over first.

8
00:00:45,600 --> 00:00:47,000
You little brat!

9
00:00:47,039 --> 00:00:48,640
I'll kill him right now, I swear!

10
00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:50,000
Throw the weapons over here.

11
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:51,079
Or I'll kill him.

12
00:00:51,759 --> 00:00:52,600
You... you...

13
00:00:55,479 --> 00:00:56,280
Hurry up!

14
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:05,640
Okay.

15
00:01:07,519 --> 00:01:08,239
Fatty!

16
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:10,519
Why should we let him go?

17
00:01:10,959 --> 00:01:12,079
I'll just slit his throat right now.

18
00:01:12,079 --> 00:01:12,959
Wouldn't that solve it?

19
00:01:12,959 --> 00:01:15,239
Don't be reckless. She's worked up.

20
00:01:15,239 --> 00:01:16,159
Just play along with her for now.

21
00:01:16,159 --> 00:01:17,040
Calm her down first.

22
00:01:17,079 --> 00:01:17,879
Hurry up!

23
00:01:20,159 --> 00:01:20,560
Give it to her.

24
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,280
Give it to me.

25
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:25,239
The crossbow. Here.

26
00:01:30,519 --> 00:01:31,319
Let Old Lu go.

27
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:33,239
Let my godfather go too.

28
00:01:35,439 --> 00:01:38,280
Old Chen, you have to save me!

29
00:01:38,439 --> 00:01:39,079
Hurry up!

30
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:40,239
Let Old Lu go.

31
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:41,599
Let's release them together.

32
00:01:41,599 --> 00:01:42,959
Okay, together.

33
00:01:44,079 --> 00:01:46,280
One, two.

34
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:05,000
The tables have turned, you know.

35
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:05,879
What do you want?

36
00:02:06,439 --> 00:02:08,319
I just want the Lingxiao Pearl.

37
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,919
As long as you help me get the pearl

38
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:12,479
and ensure I leave unharmed,

39
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:15,159
I'll naturally let Old Lu go.

40
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:17,080
Don't say I didn't warn you.

41
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:19,039
The Lingxiao Pearl holds an unknown energy.

42
00:02:19,039 --> 00:02:20,120
None of us knows what it is.

43
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,520
If you just take it like this,

44
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:22,800
aren't you afraid it could be dangerous?

45
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,800
Brother Chen,

46
00:02:24,759 --> 00:02:26,439
single-handedly,

47
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:29,719
you brought this rare treasure to light.

48
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:33,560
Why hand it over to the state?

49
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,039
Compared to those tourists,

50
00:02:35,039 --> 00:02:38,240
I know its historical value far better.

51
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:42,599
Shouldn't it belong in my hands?

52
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:43,280
I believe

53
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:45,479
you can train your own archaeologists.

54
00:02:45,879 --> 00:02:48,560
But I trust the state archaeologists more.

55
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:51,400
They put history and civilization first.

56
00:02:51,599 --> 00:02:54,080
Their expertise isn't just their skill,

57
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,560
but their attitude toward history

58
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,919
and the spread of human culture.

59
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,080
Furthermore,

60
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:04,719
if you collect these artifacts yourself,

61
00:03:05,039 --> 00:03:06,159
do you really call that protection?

62
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,879
For archaeologists,

63
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,639
preserving artifacts is just the basics.

64
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,280
Exploring the history and civilization

65
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,719
that an artifact reveals,

66
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:15,080
that's an archaeologist's lifelong pursuit.

67
00:03:15,639 --> 00:03:17,680
Uncle Min, because of your personal motives,

68
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:19,879
a piece of history is lost and left blank.

69
00:03:19,879 --> 00:03:20,840
Do you really think you're more qualified

70
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,360
than the state to keep it?

71
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:25,479
Fatty, you little punk!

72
00:03:25,479 --> 00:03:26,759
You think I'm blind?

73
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:28,919
Take one more step forward,

74
00:03:28,919 --> 00:03:29,479
and trust me,

75
00:03:29,479 --> 00:03:31,879
you can take Old Lu's head back with you.

76
00:03:31,879 --> 00:03:32,639
Get back!

77
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,479
Fatty, it's no use.

78
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,479
Step back.

79
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,599
Brother Chen, all that talk

80
00:03:42,599 --> 00:03:43,400
is just to keep me

81
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:45,240
from getting the Lingxiao Pearl, right?

82
00:03:45,479 --> 00:03:47,000
I just hope you consider it carefully.

83
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:47,879
You...

84
00:03:48,639 --> 00:03:50,759
Are you really willing to die

85
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:53,039
for your archaeology team?

86
00:03:53,479 --> 00:03:55,039
Of course I want to live.

87
00:03:55,479 --> 00:03:56,879
Then what about your brother's life?

88
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:57,719
Uncle Min,

89
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:58,599
wait a moment.

90
00:03:58,879 --> 00:04:00,599
We can't wait any longer, An Xiang.

91
00:04:01,159 --> 00:04:02,360
Coming to this altar,

92
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:03,599
I just realized

93
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:06,319
I read it in the Book of Mengna Valley,

94
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,240
the records of the Mengna Valley queen

95
00:04:08,319 --> 00:04:10,039
performing the sacrificial ceremony.

96
00:04:10,319 --> 00:04:11,520
Their sacrificial ceremony

97
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,840
probably wasn't for worshipping gods.

98
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,919
It was to seek the pearl's deeper secrets.

99
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:16,800
Deeper secrets?

100
00:04:17,439 --> 00:04:18,240
Godfather,

101
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:21,240
remember the murals we saw earlier?

102
00:04:21,879 --> 00:04:23,519
Mengna Valley's rapid rise

103
00:04:24,319 --> 00:04:26,519
was likely tied to this Lingxiao Pearl.

104
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,839
Think about it, back in that era,

105
00:04:29,959 --> 00:04:31,399
they already mastered astronomy.

106
00:04:31,879 --> 00:04:32,680
It's very possible

107
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,360
they wanted to discover more

108
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:36,319
secrets of the universe from the pearl.

109
00:04:37,279 --> 00:04:38,600
Since the Lingxiao Pearl

110
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,800
is right here before us,

111
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,360
why don't we give it a try?

112
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:44,920
Maybe we can truly unlock its secrets.

113
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:10,120
And then?

114
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,480
The Book of Mengna Valley says

115
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:22,120
that circular platform

116
00:05:22,319 --> 00:05:24,399
is closest to the center of the universe.

117
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,199
Godfather,

118
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:26,759
why don't you step over there?

119
00:05:31,879 --> 00:05:33,240
Of course I will.

120
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,040
If you won't go,

121
00:05:38,519 --> 00:05:39,480
I'll go with you.

122
00:05:55,079 --> 00:05:56,839
Just, just now,

123
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:59,000
when An Xiang was threatening me,

124
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:03,639
she secretly told me to trust her.

125
00:06:03,879 --> 00:06:05,800
Bro, can you use your head?

126
00:06:06,279 --> 00:06:08,439
Someone holds a knife to your neck

127
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:09,439
and tells you to trust her,

128
00:06:09,439 --> 00:06:10,120
and you believe it?

129
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:15,079
Bro.

130
00:06:15,199 --> 00:06:16,279
Get up.

131
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,040
I'm thinking,

132
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,920
maybe An Xiang really has feelings for me.

133
00:06:20,319 --> 00:06:21,800
What goes on inside this woman's head

134
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:23,199
is just a total mess.

135
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:24,120
Yes, yes, yes.

136
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:26,319
No, no, no.

137
00:06:27,759 --> 00:06:28,920
How, how did you get out?

138
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:29,839
Doing magic tricks?

139
00:06:30,399 --> 00:06:31,279
I have a small knife.

140
00:06:32,759 --> 00:06:33,519
Where'd you get it?

141
00:06:33,839 --> 00:06:36,560
When An Xiang was threatening me,

142
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:37,920
she secretly slipped it to me.

143
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,240
How could I not believe her?

144
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:56,519
Old Lu, what else did An Xiang say?

145
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:57,720
It was urgent.

146
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:58,600
She didn't say anything else.

147
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:01,680
Who knows what that little girl is up to.

148
00:07:01,879 --> 00:07:04,720
I bet An Xiang has an eyeball scar too.

149
00:07:05,879 --> 00:07:07,160
She has one too?

150
00:07:08,439 --> 00:07:10,639
I noticed that as we approached the altar,

151
00:07:10,759 --> 00:07:12,439
her body started reacting.

152
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,639
An Xiang, An Xiang.

153
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:15,639
You okay? What's wrong?

154
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,079
I, I...

155
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,519
My wound hurts a little.

156
00:07:19,399 --> 00:07:20,120
Also,

157
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:23,160
once I wanted to check her wound,

158
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,759
but Uncle Min interrupted.

159
00:07:24,879 --> 00:07:25,759
"Take off her jacket,

160
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:26,839
I'll check her wound."

161
00:07:27,319 --> 00:07:27,920
"No need,

162
00:07:28,319 --> 00:07:29,120
I can handle it."

163
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:34,040
So I think

164
00:07:34,199 --> 00:07:36,399
Uncle Min just didn't want you to see

165
00:07:36,399 --> 00:07:37,800
that eyeball scar of hers.

166
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:38,839
It's possible.

167
00:07:39,439 --> 00:07:40,319
Could it be

168
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:43,120
Uncle Min was so desperate for the pearl

169
00:07:43,879 --> 00:07:45,360
all because of An Xiang?

170
00:07:51,959 --> 00:07:52,759
An Xiang.

171
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,720
So what should we do next?

172
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:09,240
Let's go.

173
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:13,959
The book says

174
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:16,040
all things, life and death,

175
00:08:16,199 --> 00:08:17,279
follow the cycle of cause and effect.

176
00:08:17,759 --> 00:08:19,720
Godfather, are you ready?

177
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:23,560
Why are you pointing a crossbow at me?

178
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:25,399
Don't you know

179
00:08:25,399 --> 00:08:27,160
that all of this was for you?

180
00:08:27,399 --> 00:08:28,120
If it weren't for the fact

181
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,560
that I carry the Mengna Valley gene,

182
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,199
would you ever have adopted me?

183
00:08:33,519 --> 00:08:35,519
To find clues about the Lingxiao Pearl,

184
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,879
you killed my real parents

185
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,840
and raised me by your side

186
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:42,080
just so you could use me later, right?

187
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,159
I treated you

188
00:08:48,159 --> 00:08:50,159
as my only family in this world.

189
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:53,200
I knew you'd done many terrible things,

190
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:56,720
but every time, I convinced myself

191
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:58,240
to believe you were a good man.

192
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,840
Even when you killed Auntie He.

193
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:02,840
But I never imagined

194
00:09:03,399 --> 00:09:04,200
that in the end,

195
00:09:04,799 --> 00:09:06,720
I was nothing but a pawn to you.

196
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:09,919
I could have grown up happily

197
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,519
beside my real parents.

198
00:09:12,639 --> 00:09:14,519
You're the one who made me an orphan,

199
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,720
who made me call a murderer "father."

200
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:19,279
You're nothing but a killer.

201
00:09:19,399 --> 00:09:21,320
Today, I have to kill you!

202
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:21,960
An Xiang!

203
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:24,759
Stay back!

204
00:09:25,679 --> 00:09:27,080
I know you want revenge,

205
00:09:28,279 --> 00:09:30,720
but the law should punish his crimes.

206
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:31,720
If you kill him,

207
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,200
then you become a murderer too.

208
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:35,440
Brother Lu, don't say anything more.

209
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,399
I will kill him today, no matter what.

210
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,879
An Xiang, listen to me.

211
00:09:38,919 --> 00:09:40,600
We've come this far together,

212
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:42,399
through all kinds of hardship,

213
00:09:42,399 --> 00:09:43,759
all to obtain the Lingxiao Pearl.

214
00:09:43,799 --> 00:09:45,120
It's almost within our grasp.

215
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,120
I, Lian Ximin,

216
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:48,240
my lifelong wish

217
00:09:49,039 --> 00:09:51,519
is to unlock the Lingxiao Pearl's secrets.

218
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:55,039
And letting you live happily,

219
00:09:55,039 --> 00:09:56,240
saving your life,

220
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:58,960
is also the most important part

221
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,919
of unlocking the Pearl's secrets.

222
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:06,519
Since you're set on killing me,

223
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:09,279
fine.

224
00:10:15,519 --> 00:10:18,000
I'll grant your wish, An Xiang.

225
00:10:20,519 --> 00:10:21,879
But before you kill me,

226
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,519
I hope you can

227
00:10:24,799 --> 00:10:26,720
grant me just one more request.

228
00:10:28,039 --> 00:10:28,840
What is it?

229
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,600
I just want,

230
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,799
before I die,

231
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,039
to let me

232
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,879
touch it one more time,

233
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,279
the Lingxiao Pearl.

234
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,720
It's like Mengna Valley's end in my dream,

235
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:05,919
exactly the same!

236
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:06,799
Go, now!

237
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:07,759
Run!

238
00:12:07,759 --> 00:12:08,559
Grab the bag!

239
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,240
Move!

240
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:10,919
Hurry!

241
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:12,200
Get going!

242
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:22,360
Go, move it!

243
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:24,279
Two Lingxiao Pearls were lost this way.

244
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:26,240
Are we just going to leave it behind?

245
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:27,720
It survived Mengna Valley's destruction back then.

246
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:28,720
It'll be fine this time too.

247
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:29,799
Let's go! We'll figure it out outside!

248
00:13:30,399 --> 00:13:31,000
Wait a moment!
